item.title: Amazing Koala Encounter
item.description:
Amazing Koala Encounter

Amazing Koala Encounter Vlog: 22 After visiting the Koala Walk on Kangaroo Island we experienced an amazing encounter with one of the Koalas. The Koala was very comfortable around us and came down the tree and walked right in front of Emma. The sanctuary didn't joke by calling it a Koala walk.

item.title: Cinematic Sessions // A Journey Through Japan
item.description:
Cinematic Sessions // A Journey Through Japan

The country that has stolen my heart. This is the first CINEMATIC SESSIONS series of DAVODAYS. Cinematic sessions will be highlighted travel, documentary and profile videos of the the highest quality. This episode is dedicated to an amazing experience travelling through Japan over two weeks. Japan is such an incredible place to travel.

item.title: Great Ocean Road // THE TWELVE APOSTLES
item.description:
Great Ocean Road // THE TWELVE APOSTLES

Great Ocean Road // The Twelve Apostles Vlog: 18 The great ocean road is one of Australia's best coastline to drive, stunning views await as you twist and turn along the roads. The twelve apostles are one of australia's most iconic landscapes.

item.title: Snake Encounter Kangaroo Island
item.description:
Snake Encounter Kangaroo Island

Snake Encounter Kangaroo Island Vlog: 19 Emma and I decided to head out to kangaroo island for 6 nights and see what its all about. The very first night was super exciting with an awesome tiger snake encounter. This vlog is filmed a bit different with some cinematic montages throughout the vlog.
